metaface.server
Class VHMLSemantics

java.lang.Object
  metaface.server.VHMLSemantics
class VHMLSemantics
extends Object

This class is designed to interpret VHML facial elements and render using MPEG-4 FAPs. This class can be extended to allow different interpretations of VHML documents.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Simon Beard
See Also:
VHMLParser, VHMLReader
